---
title: Andrew Northall - Images
description: A selection of photographs that I have taken.
layout: default
permalink: /photography/
custom-javascript-list:
  - "https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"
  - "https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js"
  - "/js/photoswipe.min.js"
  - "/js/photoswipe-ui-default.min.js"
  - "/js/simple-photo-gallery-main.js"
custom-css-list:
  - "/css/gallery-main.css"
  - "/css/gallery-photoswipe.css"
  - "/css/photoswipe-default-skin.css"
---

{% comment %}
<div class="row">
  <div class="col">
    <h1 class="display-4">Photography</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        These are a few (or rather, just over 80) images that I have taken over the last five or so years.
    </p>
    <p>
        The images below were taken in a variety of locations, including the United Kingdom, the Caribbean, Spain,
        Germany, Hungary, Poland, Austria, France, Cyprus, Norway, Denmark, Sweden, and more.
        Some were taken with my phone but most were taken with my 
        <a target="_blank" href="https://www.nikon.co.uk/en_GB/product/discontinued/digital-cameras/2018/d3300-black">
        Nikon D3300 DSLR</a> with the stock 18-55mm lens. Thanks for looking!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
{% endcomment %}

<div class="row">
  <div class="col gallery">
    {% set index = namespace(value=0) %}
    {% for image in images %}
    <a href="/images/gallery/photos/{{ image.name }}"
      class="gallery-photo"
      data-index="{{ index.value }}"
      data-type="{{ image.type }}"
      data-gallery="0"
      data-width="{{ image.size[0] }}"
      data-height="{{ image.size[1] }}"
      data-date="{{ image.date }}"
      style="--w: {{ image.thumbnail_size[0] }}; --h: {{ image.thumbnail_size[1] }}">
      <img src="/images/gallery/thumbnails/{{ image.name }}" class="thumbnail rounded" alt="{{ image.description }}"/>
    </a>
    {% set index.value = index.value + 1 %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<div class="pswp" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="pswp__bg"></div>
  <div class="pswp__scroll-wrap">
    <div class="pswp__container">
      <div class="pswp__item"></div>
      <div class="pswp__item"></div>
      <div class="pswp__item"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden">
      <div class="pswp__top-bar">
        <div class="pswp__counter"></div>
        <button class="pswp__button pswp__button--close" title="Close (Esc)"></button>
        <button class="pswp__button pswp__button--share" title="Share"></button>
        <button class="pswp__button pswp__button--fs" title="Toggle fullscreen"></button>
        <button class="pswp__button pswp__button--zoom" title="Zoom in/out"></button>

        <div class="pswp__preloader">
          <div class="pswp__preloader__icn">
            <div class="pswp__preloader__cut">
              <div class="pswp__preloader__donut"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pswp__share-modal pswp__share-modal--hidden pswp__single-tap">
        <div class="pswp__share-tooltip"></div>
      </div>

      <button class="pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--left" title="Previous (arrow left)"></button>
      <button class="pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--right" title="Next (arrow right)"></button>

      <div class="pswp__caption">
        <div class="pswp__caption__center"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
